%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.19/trustyai-explainability.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KServe as KServe Inference Logger
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>(KServe/ModelMesh)<br/>gRPC
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC/MinIO/MariaDB)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring

    Note over ModelMesh,TrustyAI: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Processing
    ModelMesh->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>80/TCP HTTP, No Auth
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store inference data<br/>File I/O / JDBC:3306 / HTTP:9000
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP, Bearer Token (SA)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir gauges

    Note over KServe,TrustyAI: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Processing
    KServe->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent (inference request)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    KServe->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent (inference response)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store reconciled payload<br/>File I/O / JDBC / HTTP

    Note over User,ModelServer: Flow 3: Explainability Request
    User->>TrustyAI: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>80/TCP HTTP, No Auth
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Load historical data
    TrustyAI->>ModelServer: ModelInfer (gRPC)<br/>KServe v2 Protocol, TLS configurable
    ModelServer-->>TrustyAI: Inference Response
    TrustyAI-->>User: LIME Explanation (JSON)<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Scheduled Fairness Metrics
    User->>TrustyAI: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>80/TCP HTTP (schedule request)
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Scheduler triggers periodically
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read inference data<br/>File I/O / JDBC:3306
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute SPD/DIR metrics
    Note right of TrustyAI: Publishes as Micrometer gauge<br/>trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metric values
